1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 Nf6 {This is known as the Berlin Defense. It 
currently enjoys immense popularity at the elite level because of its drawish 
reputation and has become the main alternative to 3...a6. Hence, it has been 
given the nickname'the Berlin Wall.'} 4. O-O {White remains flexible by 
castling. Now Black has two choices: he can go into the Berlin endgame by taking 
on e4, or he can play classically with 4...Bc5.} *

