advantage as well as the better pawn structure.} exd4 5. O-O {It doesn't hurt to 
castle.} c6 {Black attacks the bishop. This does not help him much however.} 6. 
Bc4 {The bishop drops back.} Nf6 7. Re1 {White guards the pawn.} d6 8. c3 {White 
has nice position.} *

